snippet.textDisplay:
Plot twist, the loonaverse takes place in an isane asylum. Heejin thinks shes french but shes russian. Hyunjin sees cats, Yeojin talks to frogs, Haseul thinks shes a bird, Choerry is bipolar, Yves is obsessed w apples, Chuu is a serial stalker,Gowon thinks shes a princess, Olivia is an arsonist who wants to burn herself. Hence titles like Chaotic, Loonatic. Eden is the asylum. They escape in High Hi, recruit a feminist army in Butterfly And using vivis robotics, kim lips speed and jinsouls teleportation, they bring forth the apocolypse in so what. #StanLoona






P.S. to anybody who feels im making fun of mental illness. This whole post was made as satire, their was no seriousness behind this at all. my condolences to anyone who does suffer from mental illness. but this theory was not meant to be taken literal; i simply spun the concept of each MV and in Choerrys mv she has 2 personalities, so for it to fit w the narrative of being in an insane asylum, i jokingly claimed she has bipolar. i wont retract my comment because this was simply meant as a harmless joke.
